                               org.bukkit.inventory.ItemStack equipment)
        Queues the change of an item slot using the protocol lib item slot enum wrapper directly. If you don't want to use protocol lib as a dependency, use queue(int, ItemStack) with the item slot numbers defined at the top of this class.
        Parameters:
        itemSlot - The item slot the modification should take place.
        equipment - The item which should be placed at the specific slot.
